Description:
    Install Folio MCP (Model Context Protocol) server for AI integration.

    This generator will:
    - Create config/initializers/folio_mcp.rb with default configuration
    - Create .cursor/mcp.json.sample for Cursor IDE configuration
    - Add MCP route to config/routes.rb
    - Create migration to add MCP token columns to folio_users table

Example:
    rails generate folio:mcp:install

    This will create:
        config/initializers/folio_mcp.rb
        .cursor/mcp.json.sample
        db/migrate/XXXXXXXX_add_mcp_to_folio_users.rb
